1️⃣ Project Title
Retail Sales Analysis Using SQL
________________________________________
2️⃣ Project Description
Example:
This project analyzes retail sales data using SQL.
The goal is to extract business insights such as top customers, best-selling products, revenue by category, and monthly sales trends.
________________________________________
3️⃣ Database Schema
Explain your tables.
Customers
Column	Description
customer_id	Unique customer identifier
customer_name	Customer name
city	Customer location
Products
Column	Description
product_id	Unique product identifier
product_name	Name of product
category	Product category
price	Product price
Orders
Column	Description
order_id	Unique order identifier
customer_id	Customer who placed the order
product_id	Product purchased
quantity	Number of items
order_date	Date of purchase
________________________________________
4️⃣ Key Business Questions
Example:
•	Who are the top spending customers?
•	Which products generate the most revenue?
•	Which city generates the highest sales?
•	What are the monthly sales trends?
•	Which products sell the most?
________________________________________
5️⃣ SQL Skills Used
•	SELECT
•	WHERE
•	ORDER BY
•	GROUP BY
•	HAVING
•	INNER JOIN
•	Aggregate Functions (SUM, AVG, COUNT, MAX, MIN)
